ğŸ•¹Â Usage

### 1Â Â Run in paperÂ modeÂ (default)

```bash
pnpm dev                     # 5â€‘minute paper loop
tail -f logs/agent.log       # stream structured logs
```

The bot logs every FeatureVector, selector decision, and TradeIntent without signing any transaction.

### 2Â Â Switch to live trading

```bash
export PAPER=false           # or set in .env
docker secret create WALLET_KEY /path/privkey.hex
docker compose up            # hotâ€‘reloads with live signing
```

> **Reminder**Â â€“ fund the wallet with native gas (ETH) and turn on a hardware wallet for size â‰¥Â $10â€¯k.

### 3Â Â Pause / resume

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/admin/pause    # stop new trades
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/admin/resume   # resume loop
```

### 4Â Â Retrain DriftBrain

```bash
docker compose exec driftbrain python train.py --n_trials 10000
# New model saved to /models and autoâ€‘reloaded by the Node agent
```

### 5Â Â Customise strategies

Edit any file in `src/strategy/`, then:

```bash
pnpm test && pnpm dev
```

The agent hotâ€‘reloads modules on change (ts-node-dev).

